reviews.text: This is a world class exhibition centre. Places like Starbucks, Pacific, 7eleven and some Chinese restaurants are perfect for your snacking needs. The bathrooms are well maintained and clean. There is really nothing else around, so make sure you are really interested in the expo otherwise you will have a dreary time.
This place is huge, best thing is you can reach here dieectly by express train

For those who need the information: as of 2019, there is a subway, starbucks, 7 eleven when you first enter. Further inside are 2-3 restaurants opendd by asia world. Not too expensive if you can afford tickets.
